      "updated": 1779100399465,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Translate Chinese to English:\n\n人在江湖，身不由己。 -> In the\nmartial arts world, one cannot\nalways control one's own destiny.\n他轻功极高，踏雪无痕。 -> His\nlightness skill is unparalleled; he\nleaves no trace when treading on\nsnow.\n他练功太急，结果走火入魔了。 ->\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "pA1MK_g_uJ0xZYk6v-mTc",
      "originalText": "Translate Chinese to English:\n\n人在江湖，身不由己。 -> In the martial arts world, one cannot always control one's own destiny.\n他轻功极高，踏雪无痕。 -> His lightness skill is unparalleled; he leaves no trace when treading on snow.\n他练功太急，结果走火入魔了。 ->\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
